tibackuplib-dev (0.9.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Ship headers + CMake package config for tibackuplib 0.9.2. Catches the -dev
    package up from 0.8.3 (it was not bumped for 0.9.0/0.9.1): now includes
    sshClient::mkdir, tiBackupMailer (SMTP incl. TLS/STARTTLS/SSL), the scheduler,
    and the umount_after_backup job field. Tracks the runtime library version.

